Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從第一眼看到她我就喜歡上她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信真由美的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓起勇氣向她要求交往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起我無法答應您的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我拚命的告訴她夢與占卜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於打動她的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣我與綾女開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了 快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會的 綾女我…很高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺 太難以置信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 難道你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真由美你覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呀 真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試著分析剛才你講的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那是你和綾女的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啦 我是跟你講比如啦 比如
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不提那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為這種不可思議的事應該如何解釋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巧合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣你們都成為那種關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於一直喜歡你的我來說是很痛苦的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你說的是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個人太單純了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，我是池花木綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才跟她握手時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個感覺到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 你怎麼了 水煮開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟夢中的我一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 我不敢回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你連那個都查了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡有點在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你不是承認自己前輩子是叫做源四郎的士兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢中的綾女與現實中的綾女一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而關於舊神社的記錄中也出現好幾次綾女的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從戰國時代之後一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎大人一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們發誓要在一起的 我不能夠死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎大人 源四郎大人 請振作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎大人 請振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的 傳說那家神社的神官一族會使不老不死之術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果綾女是被施了法術的一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你遇到的可能就是前輩子的情人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 看到了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次你說我的前輩子是做與神明有關的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 果然一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看到你的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巫女的打扮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是巫女的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！與高影的女友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什麼時代的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰國時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰國時代？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，應該是江戶時代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明治 昭和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了 應該已經死了呀 我是占卜你的前世的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有死？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那麼認真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜本來就是不科學的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太驚人了綾女的這裡濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭…別那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 高影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 您插到我的底部了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎您插到我的底部了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好、好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體好麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能有那麼奇怪的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐 請您再重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐 您願意聽我的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和高影共度人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起老去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐 您不可以操之過急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不慎重一點的話以後就很難挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經活太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她應該能接受現在的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只能看著他年老死去 自己的模樣卻毫無改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這種事我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和他共度相同的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後和他…和他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女小姐 別做傻事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您已經失敗一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果又重蹈覆轍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算您成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施用兩次法術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將無法承受那個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會化成灰燼而死掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在下次滿月的時候執行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再等下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都聽到你的呻吟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧 你是不是在擔心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 綾女和我 誰比較重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡說什麼呀 你是我妹妹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能和綾女比較的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜綾女會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，現在還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快點去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 你是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那麼多 哥 快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我搞不懂整件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件大事在發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要平安無事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 綾女呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高影大人 綾女不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到綾女的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 綾女在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高影大人 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不能再進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底在裡面做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 現在正在執行神聖的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在結束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都不能踏入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您打破規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會發生可怕的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會毀滅與消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以去呀 不可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 我不會讓你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女 你沒事吧 振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎大人 我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到你…已經很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也沒有遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女！綾女！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高影那小子 感冒還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到高影還好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到她我就寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去探病怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們恢復了自然就會出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你相處的感覺也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 那天你怎麼知道綾女會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女在戰國時代的戀人是叫做源四郎的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是夢中的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎是哥哥的前世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女為了拯救受傷的源四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施用了不老不死術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻搞錯了施在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而活到這個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而遇到哥哥以後也就是源四郎的轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就開始希望與你一起老去 死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她又施了法術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想解開法力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是儀式卻失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法術解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾女終於死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法和我想愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她幹嘛施那種儀式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許你不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個綾女就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是綾女的轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算曾經發生很多不可思議的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是轉世的和前世的人是不可能同時存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道道理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我在綾女死亡的19年前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受生命 轉世到這個社會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道擁有同樣靈魂的人同時存在是很矛盾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是時間不見得是永遠向未來流動的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以什麼事都可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實本來就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這個解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了讓人難以相信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個夜晚 我夢到了綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前世的我 死去的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.15,0:22:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是滿月的夜晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那天夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舉行儀式的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不就無法解除不老不死之術了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣綾女不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是她的轉世那你不就不存在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能從世界上消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你還要阻止綾女的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道可能有人會死掉我不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 所以那時候你才問我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子與綾女 誰比較重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我應該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此才問哥哥 讓我最重要的人替我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很難相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我確信舞子與我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:23:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩子是戰國時代的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源四郎與綾女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了履行四百幾十年前的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 就要結合了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這麼做可能有點違背爸爸的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.67,0:24:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.68,0:24:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不習慣的話就像以前那樣喊我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.06,0:25:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺很好哦 舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.93,0:25:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 別折磨我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.10,0:25:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.61,0:25:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.96,0:25:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.47,0:25:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我想早點和哥哥合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.82,0:26:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道嗎 要插了哦 舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.99,0:26:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.82,0:26:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛嗎 舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.00,0:26:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就隨你的意移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.70,0:26:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺如何 舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.54,0:26:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體裡面好熱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱好熱 快融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.72,0:26:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 還要 還要 再插
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.73,0:26:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 不行了 這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.24,0:26:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會瘋掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.46,0:27:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.63,0:27:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 我也快射了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.30,0:27:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.64,0:27:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.21,0:28:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞子 你看看
